*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT ZPOLYMORPHISM.

class poly definition.  " Declares a class named poly with a data attribute message and a method display.
  public section.
  data: message type string.
  methods:display.
  endclass.

  class poly implementation. " Implements the methods of the class poly. The display method sets a message and writes it to the output.
    method:display.
      message = ' i am using polymorphism'.
      write : message color  3 intensified off.
      endmethod.
    endclass.

    class poly1 definition inheriting from poly. "Declares a class named poly1 that inherits from poly. It redefines the display method
      public section.
      methods display redefinition.
      endclass.

     class poly1 implementation. "Implements the redefined display method for the class poly1.
    method:display.
      message = ' i am using polymorphism child class'.
      write : message color  6 intensified off.
      endmethod.
    endclass.

    class polychild definition inheriting from poly. " Declares a class named polychild that inherits from poly. It also redefines the display method.
      public section.
      methods:display redefinition.
      endclass.

        class polychild  implementation." Implements the redefined display method for the class polychild.
     method:display.
      message = ' i am using  child class'.
      write : message color  4 intensified off.
      endmethod.
    endclass.

    start-of-selection.  "beginning of the executable part of the program.
    write:'poly class section'.
    uline.  " Outputs a header and underlines it to separate sections.

    skip.
        data:obj type ref to poly.  "Declares a reference variable obj of type poly.
        create object obj."Creates an object of class poly and assigns it to obj.
        call method obj->display.   "Calls the display method of the object obj. The same structure is repeated for poly1 and polychild classes with objects obj1 and obj2 respectively.
    skip.

    uline.
    write:'poly1 class section'.
    uline.

    skip.
    data:obj1 type ref to poly1.
         create object obj1.
         call method obj1->display.
    skip.
    skip.
    uline.
    write:'child class section'.
    skip.
    data:obj2 type ref to polychild.
       create object obj2.
       call method obj2->display.
